    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115480/extras/717217a6eb1fe0c182dde2eb3d7ca267.avif?t=1767580759\" width=800 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115480/extras/74d92c4ae6b43bcaa2e9a315ba0e141e.poster.avif?t=1767580759\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115480/extras/74d92c4ae6b43bcaa2e9a315ba0e141e.webm?t=1767580759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115480/extras/74d92c4ae6b43bcaa2e9a315ba0e141e.mp4?t=1767580759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhance and <strong>Upgrade</strong> your gear at the Blacksmith. Every <strong>Tether</strong> weapon has a unique passive that changes your gameplay, and you may <strong>Modify</strong> your weapons to suit your strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115480/extras/081b8460a14d4e332b830dfeea1e7299.avif?t=1767580759\" width=800 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115480/extras/f075b292c30cf6418631991636b76947.poster.avif?t=1767580759\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115480/extras/f075b292c30cf6418631991636b76947.webm?t=1767580759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115480/extras/f075b292c30cf6418631991636b76947.mp4?t=1767580759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create <strong>strategic builds</strong> by selecting Tethers to wield, slotting them into your inventory, and forming a network of powerful <strong>Gear Modifiers</strong> to ensure victory.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115480/extras/22621c4468004e29acc8b44d4fb2a10a.avif?t=1767580759\" width=800 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115480/extras/c823691df9fce5696e02c1bb67af91fe.poster.avif?t=1767580759\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115480/extras/c823691df9fce5696e02c1bb67af91fe.webm?t=1767580759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115480/extras/c823691df9fce5696e02c1bb67af91fe.mp4?t=1767580759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in complex first person turn based combat against a <strong>variety of dangerous enemies</strong>. <strong>Sequence</strong> your skills and learn each enemy’s strategy. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115480/extras/62fc3213454cc9e3773170e82a893be7.avif?t=1767580759\" width=800 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115480/extras/260e61dc1aaab5b1bf720933e84e13c7.poster.avif?t=1767580759\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115480/extras/260e61dc1aaab5b1bf720933e84e13c7.webm?t=1767580759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115480/extras/260e61dc1aaab5b1bf720933e84e13c7.mp4?t=1767580759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore perilous dungeons and abandoned cities filled with useful gear and constant danger in an <strong>isometric third person perspective</strong>.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115480/extras/ba06b4bda8e5a000194b41a7c5a7196d.avif?t=1767580759\" width=800 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115480/extras/da68d2401090d29a673b09ba971e2b93.poster.avif?t=1767580759\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115480/extras/da68d2401090d29a673b09ba971e2b93.webm?t=1767580759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115480/extras/da68d2401090d29a673b09ba971e2b93.mp4?t=1767580759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Encounter characters at the caravan hub, or out in the wild. Utilize them for their services while <strong>learning about their past and future</strong>, and in turn, discover the <strong>dark history of the Lords</strong> and their impact on the lands. </p></li></ul>",
